Build for multiple python versions.  Patch from Matthias Klose
<doko@debian.org> via Ubuntu.  Mostly, rename libsvn_swig_py to
libsvn_swig_py2.x.

Submitted upstream: http://svn.haxx.se/dev/archive-2008-05/0361.shtml

